snippet.title: Fictorum: Three Minute Gameplay Demo
snippet.description:
A short demo of Fictorum, showcasing dynamic spell-shaping, destructible structures, itemization, and world progression. 
Fictorum is currently available action RPG for PC.

http://www.fictorum.com

Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/503620/Fictorum/
GOG: https://www.gog.com/game/fictorum
